original_title: Bronx: Henry Hudson Parkway - Kappock Street
text:
Henry Hudson Parkway, south from Kappock Street, toward the Henry Hudson Memorial Bridge, showing at the S.E. corner of the aforementioned streets, the I. G. Johnson Mansion, this being the rear of the house.

May 25, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.

original_title: Bronx: Henry Hudson Parkway - Kappock Street
text:
Henry Hudson Parkway (Spuyten Duyvil Parkway), at the S.E. corner of Kappock Street. The view is in a northerly direction.

May 25, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.

original_title: Bronx: Henry Hudson Parkway - Kappock Street
text:
Henry Hudson Parkway, north from the northern end of the Henry Hudson Memorial Bridge. The large stone mansion on the hill is at the S.E. corner of Kappock Street and is the Isaac G. Johnson Mansion.
May 25, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.

The same, showing a more prominent view of the I. G. Johnson House.
May 25, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.

The same, from a point slightly northward (the S.E. corner of Kappock Street).
May 25, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.
